node.text: The cheaper we can buy our long-term holds, the better! 💯🔥

Covid exposed this truth to many. 

When it comes down to it, companies won't hesitate to cut jobs to save money.. 

One Stream of Income = Risky.

Buy ASSETS to create more Income. 

Multiple Streams of Income = Stability.
What you do with the extra money you make determines your financial future.
People don’t want to be educated, they want to be entertained. What do you think? 🤔
